## Problem
OpenCode anthropic multi-account always uses `creds.accounts[0]`. Config still exposes `cfg_opencodeAccountIndex` (`configGeneral.qml:89-99`, `main.xml:17-19`) but nothing in the controller reads it. Multi-account OpenCode Anthropic selection is broken for any account other than the first.

## Location
contents/ui/ProfileController.qml:436-441

## Suggested fix
Pass account index from config into `extractOpencodeAuth` (and ideally model each OpenCode account as its own discovered profile).

